        <h1 class="animate__animated animate__bounce" id="about"> About</h1>
        <p class="summary">At Decibel our goal is to broaden users taste in music and allow for new discovery of music. Our creators are Gaby Nina, Angie Chirchella, Kylie Wasserman, and Genevieve Anderson. We are four students at Marist College in upstate New York. We started Decibel because we wanted to learn more about how people connect with music, and to be able to easily share music with others. We have noticed that it can be difficult to find new music, and our goal is to make that search easier. On our website you will be able to submit music that you enjoy, along with browse music that other people listen to as well. We hope that through the use of our page you are able to discover more about yourself and others through music!</p> 
